Blocks.Description: In GTFO you can find artifacts around the maps. If the "artifact heat" of a particular mission is high, the artifacts found on this mission will be valuable and can be exchanged for other valuable items. If the "artifact heat" is low, the artifacts will be less valuable. So the value of artifacts go up and down like a stock, and the term "artifact heat" represents the "exchange rate" (i.e. the current value) of the artifacts in a given mission.

Blocks.English:
Exit the expedition, leave your teammates and return to the rundown interface.

<size=90%><color=orange>NOTE: All collected artifacts will be LOST, you will <u>NOT</u> gain any boosters.</color></size>
Blocks.Description: "Expedition" is GTFO's word for "mission" or "map". "Rundown" is GTFO's word for "campaign", i.e. a set of expeditions.

Blocks.English:
<color=red><size=60>WARNING: READ BEFORE PLAYING</color></size>

This game contains flashing images, light patterns or other visual effects, which may cause epileptic symptoms, seizures, or other problems for a small percentage of players. Even people with no prior history of epileptic seizure might be affected.

<color=red>IMMEDIATELY STOP PLAYING AND CONSULT A DOCTOR IF YOU EXPERIENCE ANY DISCOMFORT</color>
Blocks.Description: A warning message about photosensitivity. Shown at the start of the game.

French.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>AVERTISSEMENT : À LIRE AVANT DE JOUER</color></size>

Ce jeu contient des images qui clignotent, des motifs lumineux ou d'autres effets visuels susceptibles de provoquer des symptômes épileptiques, des crises ou d'autres problèmes chez un faible pourcentage de joueurs. Même les personnes n'ayant aucun antécédent épileptique peuvent être affectées.

<color=red>ARRÊTEZ IMMÉDIATEMENT DE JOUER ET CONSULTEZ UN MÉDECIN SI VOUS RESSENTEZ LA MOINDRE GÊNE.</color>

Italian.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>ATTENZIONE: LEGGERE PRIMA DI GIOCARE</color></size>

Questo gioco contiene immagini lampeggianti, schemi luminosi o altri effetti visivi che possono causare sintomi epilettici, convulsioni o altri problemi a una piccola percentuale di giocatori. Anche le persone senza precedenti di crisi epilettiche potrebbero esserne colpite.

<color=red>SE SI PROVA QUALSIASI MALESSERE, SMETTERE DI GIOCARE IMMEDIATAMENTE E CONSULTARE UN MEDICO</color>

German.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>WARNUNG: VOR DEM SPIELEN LESEN</color></size>

Dieses Spiel verwendet blinkende Bilder, Lichtmuster oder andere visuelle Effekte, die bei einem kleinen Prozentsatz der Spieler epileptische Symptome, Krampfanfälle oder andere Probleme verursachen können. Auch Menschen, die noch nie einen epileptischen Anfall hatten, können davon betroffen sein.

<color=red>HÖREN SIE SOFORT AUF ZU SPIELEN UND SUCHEN SIE EINEN ARZT AUF, WENN SIE BEGINNEN, SICH UNWOHL ZU FÜHLEN.</color>

Spanish.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>AVISO: LEER ANTES DE JUGAR</color></size>

El juego contiene imágenes con destellos, luces y otros efectos visuales que pueden provocar síntomas de epilepsia, convulsiones u otro tipo de problemas para un pequeño porcentaje de jugadores. Nota: incluso personas que jamás hayan sufrido ataques ni síntomas de epilepsia podrían verse afectadas.

<color=red>DEJA DE JUGAR INMEDIATAMENTE SI EXPERIMENTAS ALGÚN TIPO DE INCOMODIDAD Y CONSULTA CON TU MÉDICO</color>

Russian.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>ПРЕДУПРЕЖДЕНИЕ. ПРОЧТИТЕ ПЕРЕД ИГРОЙ</color></size>

В игре присутствуют мигающие изображения, узоры и прочие визуальные эффекты, которые могут вызвать симптомы эпилепсии или припадки у небольшого процента пользователей. Изображения могут вызвать приступ даже у людей, ранее не страдавших эпилепсией.

<color=red>В СЛУЧАЕ ВОЗНИКНОВЕНИЯ СИМПТОМОВ НЕМЕДЛЕННО ПРЕКРАТИТЕ ИГРАТЬ И ПРОКОНСУЛЬТИРУЙТЕСЬ С ВРАЧОМ.</color>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>AVISO: LEIA ANTES DE JOGAR</color></size>

Este jogo contém imagens piscantes, padrões de luzes e outros efeitos visuais que podem causam sintomas epilépticos, convulsões ou outros problemas para um pequeno percentual de jogadores. Até mesmo indivíduos sem qualquer histórico prévio de convulsões podem ser afetados.

<color=red>PARE DE JOGAR IMEDIATAMENTE E CONSULTE UM MÉDICO SE VOCÊ SENTIR QUALQUER DESCONFORTO</color>

Polish.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>OSTRZEŻENIE: PRZECZYTAJ PRZED ROZPOCZĘCIEM GRY</color></size>

Gra zawiera migające obrazy, wzory świateł i inne efekty wizualne, które u niewielkiego odsetka graczy mogą wywoływać objawy epilepsji, napady padaczkowe oraz inne problemy. Sytuacja ta może mieć miejsce nawet u osób, u których wcześniej nie stwierdzono napadów padaczkowych.

<color=red>W RAZIE UCZUCIA DYSKOMFORTU NALEŻY NATYCHMIAST PRZERWAĆ GRĘ</color>

Japanese.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>警告：プレイする前にお読みください</color></size>

本ゲームには、ごく一部のプレイヤーにてんかん症状や発作などの問題を引き起こす可能性のある点滅する画像や光のパターンなどの視覚効果が含まれています。過去にてんかん発作を起こしたことのない方でも影響を受けることがあります。

<color=red>異常を感じた場合は、すぐにプレイをやめて医師の診察を受けてください</color>

Korean.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>경고: 게임 전 주의 사항</color></size>

이 게임에 포함된 번쩍이는 이미지, 조명 패턴 등의 시각 효과는 일부 플레이어에게 뇌전증 증상, 발작 또는 기타 문제를 일으킬 수 있습니다. 이전에 뇌전증 발작 병력이 없는 사람들도 영향을 받을 수 있습니다.

<color=red>불편함을 느끼면 즉시 게임을 중단하고 의사와 상담하십시오</color>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>警告：玩遊戲前請先閱讀</color></size>

本遊戲包含閃爍影像、光影或其他視覺效果，可能會導致一小部分玩家出現癲癇症狀、發作或其他問題。即使以前沒有癲癇發作史的人也可能受到影響。

<color=red>如果感到任何不適，請立即停止遊戲並諮詢醫生</color>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
<color=red><size=60>警告：玩前须知</color></size>

本游戏包含闪烁图像、光带或其他视觉效果，可能导致一小部分玩家产生癫痫症状、痉挛发作或其他问题。即使无癫痫痉挛史者也可能受到影响。

<color=red>若有任何不适反应，请立即停止游戏并咨询医生</color>

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key equips the player's "hacking tool", which is a handheld computer device.

Japanese.Translation: ハッキングツールを選択

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.SelectHackingTool

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key cycles through the player's inventory - each key press switches to the next piece of gear, like so: Melee weapon > primary weapon > special weapon > tool > resource pack > consumable > melee weapon
Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.ToggleGear

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key toggles the flashlight on/off.

Japanese.Translation: フラッシュライト切り替え

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.ToggleFlashlight

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key toggles the full-screen map on/off.
Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.ToggleMap

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key toggles the objective screen on/off. The objective screen contains more detailed information about your current mission objective.
Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.ToggleObjectivesScreen

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key toggles the communication menu on/off.

Japanese.Translation: 通信メニュー切り替え

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.ToggleCommmunicationMenu

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key select an option in the communication menu
Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.SelectCommmunicationMenu

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key is used to open the text chat in the HUD (in order to write messages) and then sending messages.

Japanese.Translation: テキストチャットを開く/送る

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.OpenSendTextChat

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key closes/hides the text chat in the HUD.

Japanese.Translation: テキストチャットを閉じる

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.CloseTextChat

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. To "ping" something in the surroundings is to put a marker/waypoint on it, to make your teammates aware of it.
Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.Ping

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This key makes info boxes appear above each teammate's head (in your HUD), to inform you about their health and ammo status.

French.Translation: Maintenir pour afficher les infos des coéquipiers

Italian.Translation: Tieni premuto per mostrare info compagno di squadra

Spanish.Translation: Mantener para ver información de compañeros

Russian.Translation: Удерживать, чтобы показать сведения о напарниках

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Segurar para mostrar informações do aliado

Polish.Translation: Przytrzymaj, aby pokazać informacje o członku drużyny

Japanese.Translation: 長押しでチームメイト情報を表示

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Settings.HoldToShowTeammateInfo

Blocks.Description: Control key binding/mapping. This is the key you push in order to talk to teammates via voice chat.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Chat de voz — apertar para falar

Japanese.Translation: ボイスチャット - 通話ボタン

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 語音聊天 - 隨按即說

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 语音聊天 - 按下说话

Blocks.Description: A text string that indicates to players (in an in-world manner) that the matchmaking system is in alpha (unfinished) state. Do not alter the code-like parts.

French.Translation: \\WAR#349: Système expérimental de jumelage de prisonniers détecté.

Italian.Translation: \\GUERRA#349: Sistema sperimentale di abbinamento prigionieri rilevato.

Spanish.Translation: \\GUERRA#349: Detectado prisionero experimental en el sistema de emparejamiento.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: \\WAR#349: Sistema experimental de combinação de prisioneiros detectado.

Japanese.Translation: \\警#349:試験的囚人マッチングシステムを検出。

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: \\戰爭#349:偵測到實驗囚犯配對系統。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: \\WAR#349：检测到试验性囚犯匹配系统。

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Matchmaking.Warning1

Blocks.English: #SRES_43: Segmented prisoner selection can be time consuming and the matching prisoners will have a limited social construct as a base for survival.
Blocks.Description: A text string that indicates to players (in an in-world manner) that the matchmaking system is in alpha (unfinished) state. Do not alter the code-like parts.

French.Translation: #SRES_43: La sélection des prisonniers par segmentation peut prendre un certain temps, et les prisonniers sélectionnés auront accès à une construction sociale limitée comme base de survie.

Italian.Translation: #SRES_43: La selezione frammentata dei prigionieri può richiedere molto tempo, e i prigionieri abbinati avranno un costrutto sociale limitato come base per la sopravvivenza.

German.Translation: #SRES_43: Die segmentierte Auswahl der Gefangenen kann einige Zeit beanspruchen und gefundene Gefangene können begrenzte Überlebensgrundlagen und soziale Konstrukte besitzen.

Spanish.Translation: #SRES_43: La selección segmentada de prisioneros puede llevar mucho tiempo, y los prisioneros emparejados tendrán un constructo social limitado como base para la supervivencia.

Russian.Translation: #SRES_43: сегментированный подбор заключенных занимает длительное время. Предоставляются социальные функции, необходимые для выживания.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: #SRES_43: A seleção segmentada de prisioneiros pode demorar e a combinação de prisioneiros terá uma construção social limitada como base de sobrevivência.

Polish.Translation: #SRES_43: Segmentowana selekcja więźniów może być czasochłonna, a dopasowani więźniowie będą mieć ograniczony konstrukt społeczny jako podstawę do przetrwania.

Japanese.Translation: #SRES_43:分割された囚人選択は時間を要することがあり、またマッチした囚人の生存の基礎としての社会的構造は制限される。

Korean.Translation: #SRES_43: 수감자 선택 조건을 세분화할 경우 소요 시간이 증가할 수 있으며, 그룹 형성에도 제약이 따를 수 있음.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: #SRES_43：將囚犯選擇區段化可能會非常耗時，而且作為生存基礎的配對囚犯社會結構有限。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: #SRES_43：定向选择囚犯耗时较长，且所匹配囚犯的社会组成有限，影响生存基础。

Blocks.name: MainMenu.Matchmaking.Warning2

Blocks.English: #SRES_07: Increase survival rates by enforcing strict communication protocols
Blocks.Description: A text string that describes (in an in-world manner) that using voice chat gives players better chance of success.

French.Translation: #SRES_07: Augmentez vos chances de survie en imposant des protocoles de communication stricts.

Italian.Translation: #SRES_07: Aumenta il tasso di sopravvivenza applicando rigidi protocolli di comunicazione

German.Translation: #SRES_07: Erhöhen sie die Überlebenschance, indem Sie strenge Kommunikationsprotokolle durchsetzen

Spanish.Translation: #SRES_07: Aumenta los índices de supervivencia al reforzar los protocolos de comunicación estrictos.

Russian.Translation: #SRES_07: шанс выживания повышается благодаря более строгим протоколам взаимодействия.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: #SRES_07: Aumente as chances de sobrevivência impondo protocolos de comunicação rígidos.

Polish.Translation: #SRES_07: Zwiększ współczynnik przeżywalności poprzez egzekwowanie ścisłych protokołów komunikacyjnych

Japanese.Translation: #SRES_07:厳格な通信プロトコルを実施して生存率を上げろ

Korean.Translation: #SRES_07: 엄격한 통신 프로토콜을 적용하여 생존율을 높입니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: #SRES_07：強制執行嚴格通訊協定以提高生存率

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: #SRES_07：实施严格的通讯协议以提高生存几率

Blocks.English: You have been rewarded with {0} Booster(s) in exchange for your collected artifacts
Blocks.Description: A test that informs the player that the artifacts they collected during the last expedition/mission have been traded in for one or more boosters. The way the text combines the singular and plural version of "booster" with a parentheses around the "s" is intentional, to make Warden come across as rigid and machine-like. The "{0}" represents the number of boosters - do not alter that piece of code, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

Blocks.English: You have received {0} Booster(s) to improve your chances of survival. Use them wisely. Find and retrieve artifacts to be rewarded with additional Boosters.
Blocks.Description: A text that informs the player that the artifacts they collected during the last expedition/mission have been traded in for one or more boosters. This text is a little more descriptive and only used the very first time this happens. The way the text combines the singular and plural version of "booster" with a parentheses around the "s" is intentional, to make Warden come across as rigid and machine-like. The "{0}" represents the number of boosters - do not alter that piece of code, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

<color=red>USA POTENCIADORES</color> O <color=red>ELIMINA</color> ALGUNOS PARA HACER HUECO Y EVITAR QUE VUELVA A OCURRIRTE ESTO.

Blocks.Description: A product name for a booster (performance enhancing drug) based on an abbreviation of the word "regeneration". "C" stands for "cap".
Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.RegenerationCapShortName

Blocks.Description: Regen. is short for "health regeneration", and "cap" represents the maximum level (%) the regeneration can reach.

Blocks.Description: Describes the advantage of having a good "regeneration cap" value.

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用者的生命值恢复上限提高。

Blocks.Description: Describes the disadvantage of having a poor "regeneration cap" value.

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用者的生命值恢复上限降低。

Blocks.Description: A product name for a booster (performance enhancing drug) based on an abbreviation of the word "regeneration". "S" stands for "speed".
Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.RegenerationSpeedShortName

Blocks.Description: Regen. is short for "health regeneration", and "speed" represents speed at which the health regenerates.
Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.RegenerationSpeedName

Blocks.Description: Describes the advantage of having a good "regeneration speed" value. Essentially this means that when the subject's own health is regenerating, it will go faster than usual.

French.Translation: Le sujet régénère sa santé plus rapidement.

Italian.Translation: La salute del soggetto migliorerà più rapidamente.

Spanish.Translation: El sujeto recuperará salud más rápido.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: O indivíduo regenera saúde mais rápido.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 實驗對象生命值恢復速度較快。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用者的生命值恢复速度加快。

Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.RegenerationSpeedDescription

Blocks.Description: Describes the disadvantage of having a poor "regeneration speed" value. Essentially this means that when the subject's own health is regenerating, it will go slower than usual.

Italian.Translation: La salute del soggetto migliorerà più lentamente.

Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.RegenerationSpeedDescriptionNegative

Blocks.English: Subject will get more out of MediPacks.
Blocks.Description:
Don't localize MediPacks.

Blocks.Description: I.e. how fast the computer processor in a sentry gun works.
Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.SentryGunSpeedName

Blocks.English: Subject will overclock its sentry gun, giving it increased detection, rotation and firing speed.
Blocks.Description: Describes the advantage of having a good "sentry CPU speed" value.

French.Translation: Le sujet overclocke sa tourelle, ce qui augmente sa portée de détection, sa rotation et sa cadence de tir.

Italian.Translation: Il soggetto potenzierà la sua torretta automatica, migliorandone il rilevamento, la rotazione e la cadenza di tiro.

German.Translation: Die Versuchsperson übertaktet ihr Sentry-Geschütz und sie erhält eine erhöhte Erkennungs-, Rotations- und Feuergeschwindigkeit.

Spanish.Translation: El sujeto sobrecarga su centinela, lo que incrementará su capacidad de detección, rotación y cadencia.

Russian.Translation: Установка турели с улучшенной системой обнаружения, наведения и высокой скоростью стрельбы.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: O indivíduo acelera sua arma sentinela, dando a ela detecção, rotação e cadência de tiro melhores.

Polish.Translation: Biorca podkręci działo wartownicze, zwiększając jego wykrywalność, obroty i szybkostrzelność.

Japanese.Translation: 対象はセントリーガンをオーバークロックし、探知・回転・発射速度が向上する。

Korean.Translation: 대상이 센트리 건을 오버클럭하여 탐지, 회전 및 발사 속도를 높입니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 實驗對象可將自動砲台超頻，增加偵測、旋轉與射速。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用者将加速运行其哨戒炮，提高探测、旋转和发射速度。

Blocks.name: BoosterImplants.Effects.SentryGunSpeedDescription

Blocks.English: Subject will deploy sentry guns with decreased detection, rotation and firing speed.
Blocks.Description: Describes the disadvantage of having a poor "sentry CPU speed" value.

French.Translation: Le sujet déploie des tourelles avec une portée de détection, une rotation et une cadence de tir moins accrue.

Italian.Translation: Il soggetto schiererà torrette automatiche con rotazione, cadenza di tiro e rilevamento ridotti.

Spanish.Translation: El sujeto utilizará centinelas con menor capacidad de detección, rotación y cadencia.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: O indivíduo usa armas sentinelas com detecção, rotação e cadência de tiro reduzidas.

Polish.Translation: Biorca podkręci działo wartownicze, zmniejszając jego wykrywalność, obroty i szybkostrzelność.

Japanese.Translation: 対象は探知・回転・発射速度が低下したセントリーガンを展開する。

Korean.Translation: 대상이 설치하는 센트리 건의 탐지, 회전 및 발사 속도가 감소합니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 實驗對象部署的自動砲台會降低偵測、旋轉與射速。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用者将减速运行其哨戒炮，降低探测、旋转和发射速度。

Blocks.English: A Booster Progress value exceeding {0} will be rewarded with a random Booster from the corresponding category.
Blocks.Description: A text string that appears in the result screen (when you have failed or succeeded at an expedition.) This text explains the rules regarding how players are rewarded with boosters. The "corresponding category" bit refers to the fact that "muted" artifacts are rewarded with "muted" boosters, "bold" artifacts are rewarded with "bold" boosters and "aggressive" artifacts are rewarded with "aggressive" boosters.

French.Translation: Si votre valeur de progression de booster est supérieure à {0}, vous recevrez un booster aléatoire de la catégorie correspondante.

Italian.Translation: Un valore di avanzamento potenziamento superiore a {0} verrà ricompensato con un potenziamento casuale della categoria corrispondente.

German.Translation: Ein Booster-Fortschrittswert über {0} wird mit einem zufälligen Booster aus der entsprechenden Kategorie belohnt.

Spanish.Translation: Un valor de progreso del potenciador superior a {0} recibirá un potenciador aleatorio de la categoría correspondiente.

Russian.Translation: За прогресс с усилителями {0} вы получите случайный усилитель из соответствующей категории.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Um valor de progresso do impulso excedendo {0} será recompensado com um impulso aleatório da categoria correspondente.

Polish.Translation: Współczynnik postępów wzmacniaczy powyżej {0} zostanie nagrodzony losowym wzmacniaczem odpowiedniej kategorii.

Japanese.Translation: {0} を超えたブースター換算値には、対応するカテゴリーのランダムなブースターが与えられる。

Korean.Translation: {0}을(를) 초과하는 부스터 진행도는 해당 카테고리의 무작위 부스터로 보상됩니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 超過{0}的強化劑進度值將獲得相應的隨機強化劑獎勵。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 强化剂进度值超过{0}后，将奖励相应类别的随机强化剂。

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: TÍTULO DO PROTOCOLO DE CAMPANHA #6.0: DESTINO

Japanese.Translation: ランダウンプロトコル#6.0タイトル：目的地

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 遠征綱要協定#6.0標題：目的地

Blocks.English:
Rundown Protocol 4.5 completed. Access from section R4E1 established. Overarching objective to <color=red>probe deeper</color> remains.

Booster reward protocol in effect: Prisoners that retrieve crystal encased <color=red>artifacts</color> from around the structure will be rewarded with <color=red>Attribute Booster Modules</color>, increasing their chances of survival.

Findings from locations with high <color=red>Artifact heat</color> will be rewarded more generously.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Rundown005.SurfaceDescription

Blocks.English:
<color=orange>[STATUS]</color>OBJECTIVE STACK REITERATION 6.0. <color=red>PROBE DEEPER.</color> PRISONERS TO RESUME DESCENT AND EXPLORE UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE.

<color=orange>[APPAREL]</color>IMPROVED PSYCHOLOGICAL CONDITION OBSERVED IN PRISONERS PROVIDED WITH OPTIONAL APPAREL. PRISONERS THAT <color=red>CLEAR EXPEDITION SECTORS</color> WILL GAIN ACCESS TO SURPLUS RESOURCES.

<color=orange>[BOOSTERS]</color>BOOSTER MODULES WILL BE DISPENSED TO PRISONERS THAT <color=red>RETRIEVE CRYSTAL ENCASED ARTIFACTS.</color> OBJECTIVE STACK UPDATED.
Blocks.Description:
This is a message that shows up in a popup when the player presses the INTEL button on the RundownPage.
It is a message from the Warden and gives information about Rundown # 6.0.
In this text everything appart from the Rich Text tags should be localized, even [STATUS], [BOOSTERS] and [APPAREL].

French.Translation:
<color=orange>[STATUT]</color>RAPPEL DE LA LISTE D'OBJECTIFS 6.0. <color=red>SONDEZ PLUS EN PROFONDEUR.</color> LES PRISONNIERS DOIVENT POURSUIVRE LEUR DESCENTE ET EXPLORER JUSQU'À NOUVEL ORDRE.

<color=orange>[VÊTEMENTS]</color>AMÉLIORATION DE L'ÉTAT PSYCHOLOGIQUE OBSERVÉE CHEZ LES PRISONNIERS DOTÉS DE VÊTEMENTS FACULTATIFS. LES PRISONNIERS AYANT <color=red>ACHEVÉ LES SECTEURS D'EXPÉDITION</color> AURONT ACCÈS AUX RESSOURCES EXCÉDENTAIRES.

<color=orange>[BOOSTERS]</color>DES MODULES DE BOOSTERS SERONT ADMINISTRÉS AUX PRISONNIERS AYANT <color=red>RÉCUPÉRÉ DES ARTEFACTS COUVERTS DE CRISTAL.</color> LISTE D'OBJECTIFS MISE À JOUR.

Italian.Translation:
<color=orange>[STATO]</color>REITERAZIONE CODA OBIETTIVI 6.0. <color=red>SONDA PI PROFONDITÀ.</color> I PRIGIONIERI DEVONO RIPRENDERE LA DISCESA ED ESPLORARE FINO A NUOVO ORDINE.

<color=orange>[ABBIGLIAMENTO]</color>MIGLIORAMENTO DELLE CONDIZIONI PSICOLOGICHE OSSERVATO NEI PRIGIONIERI DOTATI DI ABBIGLIAMENTO FACOLTATIVO. I PRIGIONIERI CHE <color=red>LIBERANO I SETTORI DELLA SPEDIZIONE</color> AVRANNO ACCESSO A RISORSE IN ECCESSO.

<color=orange>[POTENZIAMENTI]</color>I MODULI DI POTENZIAMENTO SARANNO EROGATI AI PRIGIONIERI CHE <color=red>RECUPERANO MANUFATTI INCORPORATI NEL CRISTALLO.</color> STACK OBIETTIVO AGGIORNATO.

German.Translation:
<color=orange>[STATUS]</color>REITERATION DES ZIEL-STACKS 6.0. <color=red>ERFORSCHUNG VERTIEFEN.</color> DIE GEFANGENEN SOLLEN DEN ABSTIEG UND DIE ERKUNDUNG BIS AUF WEITERES FORTSETZEN.

<color=orange>[BEKLEIDUNG]</color>DIE PSYCHISCHE VERFASSUNG DER GEFANGENEN, DIE OPTIONALE BEKLEIDUNG ERHALTEN HABEN, HAT SICH VERBESSERT. GEFANGENE, DIE <color=red>EXPEDITIONSSEKTOREN RÄUMEN</color>, ERHALTEN ZUGANG ZU ÜBERSCHÜSSIGEN RESSOURCEN.

<color=orange>[BOOSTER]</color>BOOSTER-MODULE WERDEN AN GEFANGENE AUSGEGEBEN, DIE <color=red>KRISTALLENE ARTEFAKTE BERGEN</color>. ZIEL-STACK AKTUALISIERT.

Spanish.Translation:
<color=orange>[ESTADO]</color>REITERACIÓN DE ACUMULACIÓN DE OBJETIVOS 6.0. <color=red>AHONDAR MÁS.</color> LOS PRISIONEROS DEBEN RETOMAR EL DESCENSO Y EXPLORAR HASTA PRÓXIMO AVISO.

<color=orange>[INDUMENTARIA]</color>SE HA OBSERVADO UNA MEJORA EN LA SALUD PSICOLÓGICA DE LOS PRISIONEROS QUE ESCOGEN SU VESTIMENTA. LOS PRISIONEROS QUE <color=red>COMPLETEN LOS SECTORES DE EXPEDICIÓN</color> PODRÁN ACCEDER A LOS EXCEDENTES DE RECURSOS.

<color=orange>[POTENCIADORES]</color>LOS MÓDULOS DE POTENCIADORES SE ENTREGARÁN A LOS PRISIONEROS QUE <color=red>RECUPEREN CRISTALES RECUBIERTOS DE CRISTAL.</color> ACTUALIZACIÓN DE ACUMULACIÓN DE OBJETIVOS.

Russian.Translation:
<color=orange>[СТАТУС]</color>ПОВТОРНОЕ ОПИСАНИЕ ЦЕЛИ 6.0. <color=red>НУЖНО ДОПОЛНИТЕЛЬНОЕ ИЗУЧЕНИЕ.</color> ЗАКЛЮЧЕННЫЕ ОБЯЗАНЫ ВОЗОБНОВИТЬ СПУСК И ПРОДОЛЖИТЬ ИЗУЧЕНИЕ ДО ПОЛУЧЕНИЯ ДАЛЬНЕЙШИХ ИНСТРУКЦИЙ.

<color=orange>[ЭКИПИРОВКА]</color>УЛУЧШЕННЫЕ ПСИХОЛОГИЧЕСКИЕ ПОКАЗАТЕЛИ У ЗАКЛЮЧЕННЫХ, ИМЕЮЩИХ ДОПОЛНИТЕЛЬНУЮ ЭКИПИРОВКУ. ЗАКЛЮЧЕННЫЕ, КОТОРЫЕ <color=red>ЗАЧИСТЯТ ЭКСПЕДИЦИОННЫЙ СЕКТОР</color>, ПОЛУЧАТ ДОСТУП К НОВЫМ РЕСУРСАМ.

<color=orange>[УСИЛИТЕЛИ]</color>ЗАКЛЮЧЕННЫЕ, <color=red>КОТОРЫЕ ИЗВЛЕКУТ АРТЕФАКТЫ В КРИСТАЛЛИЧЕСКИХ КАПСУЛАХ</color>, ПОЛУЧАТ УСИЛИВАЮЩИЕ МОДУЛИ. ОПИСАНИЕ ЦЕЛИ ОБНОВЛЕНО.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
<color=orange>[STATUS]</color>REITERAÇÃO DE CONJUNTO DE OBJETIVOS 6.0. <color=red>SONDAGEM APROFUNDADA.</color> PRISIONEIROS RETOMAM DESCIDA E EXPLORAÇÃO ATÉ NOVO AVISO.

<color=orange>[TRAJE]</color>CONDIÇÃO PSICOLÓGICA APRIMORADA OBSERVADA EM PRISIONEIROS COM TRAJE ÓPTICO. PRISIONEIROS QUE <color=red>LIBERAM SETORES DA EXPEDIÇÃO</color> GANHAM ACESSO A RECURSOS EXCEDENTES.

<color=orange>[IMPULSOS]</color>MÓDULOS DE IMPULSO SÃO CONCEDIDOS A PRISIONEIROS QUE <color=red>RECUPERAM ARTEFATOS REVESTIDOS DE CRISTAL.</color> CONJUNTO DE OBJETIVOS ATUALIZADO.

Polish.Translation:
<color=orange>[STAN]</color>POWTÓRZENIE STOSU CELÓW 6.0. <color=red>POGŁĘBIONA SONDA.</color> WIĘŹNIOWIE POWINNI DO ODWOŁANIA WZNOWIĆ ZEJŚCIE I KONTYNUOWAĆ EKSPLORACJĘ.

<color=orange>[UBIÓR]</color>U WIĘŹNIÓW ZAOBSERWOWANO POPRAWIONY STAN PSYCHICZNY PO ZAOPATRZENIU W DODATKOWY UBIÓR. WIĘŹNIOWIE, KTÓRZY <color=red>OCZYSZCZĄ SEKTORY EKSPEDYCJI</color>, UZYSKAJĄ DOSTĘP DO NADMIAROWYCH ZASOBÓW.

<color=orange>[WZMACNIACZE]</color>WIĘŹNIOM, KTÓRZY <color=red>ZDOBĘDĄ ARTEFAKTY W KRYSZTALE</color>, PRZYZNANE ZOSTANĄ WZMACNIACZE. ZAKTUALIZOWANO STOS CELÓW.

Japanese.Translation:
<color=orange>[ステータス]</color>目標蓄積反復6.0。 <color=red>深部ヘと進め。</color> 囚人は次の通知があるまで降下と探索を続けろ。

<color=orange>[外装]</color>追加外装を与えられた囚人に精神状態の改善が見られた。<color=red>エクスペディションのセクターをクリアした</color> 囚人には余剰物資が与えられる。

<color=orange>[ブースター]</color> <color=red>クリスタルに内包されたアーティファクトを回収した</color> 囚人にはブースターモジュールが付与される。目標蓄積更新。

Korean.Translation:
<color=orange>[상태]</color>목표 목록 반복 6.0. <color=red>더 깊이 조사할 것.</color> 수감자는 추후 통보가 있을 때까지 하강을 재개하고 탐색할 것.

<color=orange>[의류]</color>선택적 의복을 제공받은 수감자에게서 심리 상태 개선이 관찰됨. <color=red>탐사 섹터를 클리어</color>하는 수감자는 잉여 자원에 접근 가능.

<color=orange>[부스터]</color>부스터 모듈은 <color=red>크리스탈에 수납된 아티팩트</color>를 회수하는 수감자에게 배포됨. 목표 목록 업데이트됨

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
<color=orange>[狀態]</color>目標堆疊重申 6.0。<color=red>進行更深入的探測。</color>

<color=orange>[服裝]</color>在提供囚犯不同服裝選擇後，觀察到的心理狀況有所改善。囚犯<color=red>清空遠征分區</color>將獲得剩餘資源。

<color=orange>[強化劑]</color>強化劑模組將分配給<color=red>取回水晶包覆寶物</color>的囚犯。目標堆疊已更新。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
<color=orange>[状态]</color>目标堆栈重复6.0。<color=red>继续深入探查。</color>囚犯继续下降探索，直至另行通知。

<color=orange>[服装]</color>据观察，配备可选服装的囚犯心理状况有所改善。<color=red>清理任务分区</color>的囚犯将获得额外资源。

<color=orange>[强化剂]</color>强化剂模块将分发给<color=red>取回红晶</color>的囚犯。目标堆栈已更新。

Blocks.English:
Floodways in lockdown, override required to allow further reconnaissance.
Unknown ceiling dwelling biomass present. Prisoners failing to exercise caution will not be considered a loss.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Expedition_1_1.Description

Blocks.English:
>...
>...[whispering] Crouch, move slowly, don't shine on them with your flashlight...
<size=200%><color=red>>...[whispering] It's pulsating - don't move!</color></size>
Blocks.Description:
Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.
[whispering] should be localized in this case.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Expedition_1_1.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
Prisoners sent to locate and retrieve hisec crate.
Unknown ceiling dwelling biomass present. Prisoners failing to exercise caution will not be considered a loss.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Expedition_1_2.Description

Blocks.English:
>...Wasn't this room empty before?
<size=200%><color=red>>...I told you those black cocoons were bad news...</color></size>
>...Fuck, I hate this place even more now.
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Expedition_1_2.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
>.. Walk soft. Flashlights off. <size=200%><color=red>Everything alerts these bastards.</color></size>
>.. We got to carry it back.
>.. I’m not touching it.
>.. Just grab the other—
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Marche doucement et éteins les torches. <size=200%><color=red>Ces salauds sont facilement alertés.</color></size>
>... On doit le ramener.
>... Pas question de toucher à ça.
>... Prends juste l'autre...

Italian.Translation:
>... Camminiamo piano. Torce spente. <size=200%><color=red>Tutto quanto allerta quei bastardi.</color></size>
>... Dobbiamo riportarlo indietro.
>... Io non lo tocco.
>... Prendi l'altro-

German.Translation:
>… Leise. Taschenlampen aus. <size=200%><color=red>Diese Bastarde werden durch alles alarmiert.</color></size>
>… Wir müssen es zurücktragen.
>… Ich fasse das nicht an.
>… Kann jemand einfach den anderen–

Spanish.Translation:
> Caminad despacio. Apagad la linterna. <size=200%><color=red>Estas sabandijas están alerta.</color></size>
> Tenemos que traerlo de vuelta.
> No voy a tocarlo.
> Recoge lo otro...

Russian.Translation:
>... Идем тихо. Свет выключить. <size=200%><color=red>Эти твари даже звук упавшей иголки услышат.</color></size>
>... Надо отнести на базу.
>... Я и пальцем не притронусь.
>... Хватайся за один—

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Caminhe lentamente. Lanterna desligada. <size=200%><color=red>Esses desgraçados são sensíveis a tudo.</color></size>
>.. Temos que carregá-lo de volta.
>.. Eu não vou colocar a mão.
>.. Só pegue o outro aí...

Polish.Translation:
>.. Poruszać się cicho. Bez latarek. <size=200%><color=red>Te gnojki są w stanie wszystko wyczuć.</color></size>
>.. Musimy to zanieść z powrotem.
>.. Nie ruszam tego.
>.. Weź tylko…

Japanese.Translation:
>.. 静かに歩け。フラッシュライトは消せ。 <size=200%><color=red>こいつらは何をしても反応する。</color></size>
>.. 持ち帰らなければならない。
>.. 触る気はない。
>.. 反対側を少しだけ…

Korean.Translation:
>.. 조심해서 걷고 플래시는 꺼. <size=200%><color=red>경고가 아주 난리도 아니군.</color></size>
>.. 갖고 돌아가야 해.
>.. 난 만지기 싫어.
>.. 닥치고 반대쪽 잡...

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…輕輕走，手電筒關掉。<size=200%><color=red>任何風吹草動都會驚醒這些混蛋。</color></size>
>…我們得搬回去。
>…我才不要碰。
>…拿另一個——

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 脚步放轻，手电筒关上。<size=200%><color=red>一丁点儿动静就会惊醒这些怪物。</color></size>
>.. 我们得把这个拿回去。
>.. 我不要碰这玩意儿。
>.. 只要抓另外——

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_1_1.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
>.. Move! MOVE! 
>.. I can't see where we're going!
>.. There’s more coming out of it! <size=200%><color=red>We gotta get away from this fucking thing!</color></size>
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Cours ! COURS ! 
>... Je vois rien !
>... Il y en a d'autres qui sortent de là ! <size=200%><color=red>On doit échapper à cette foutue bestiole !</color></size>

Italian.Translation:
>... Muoversi! MUOVERSI! 
>... Non vedo dove stiamo andando!
>... Ne vengono fuori altri! <size=200%><color=red>Dobbiamo allontanarci da questo maledetto coso!</color></size>

German.Translation:
>… Los! LOS!
>… Ich kann nicht sehen, wo wir hingehen!
>… Da kommt noch mehr! <size=200%><color=red>Wir müssen von diesem verdammten Ding weg!</color></size>

Spanish.Translation:
> ¡Moveos! ¡MOVEOS! 
> ¡No veo adónde vamos!
> ¡Están saliendo más! <size=200%><color=red>¡Tenemos que salir de esta mierda!</color></size>

Russian.Translation:
>... Живо! ЖИВО! 
>... Ни черта не видно!
>... Они лезут из всех щелей! <size=200%><color=red>Нужно поскорее отсюда выбираться!</color></size>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Rápido! RÁPIDO! 
>.. Não consigo ver para onde estamos indo!
>.. Tem mais saindo dali! <size=200%><color=red>Temos que fugir dessa merda!</color></size>

Polish.Translation:
>.. Ruchy! RUCHY! 
>.. Nie mam pojęcia, dokąd zmierzamy!
>.. Wydostaje się ich z tego jeszcze więcej! <size=200%><color=red> Musimy oddalić się od tego kurewstwa!</color></size>

Japanese.Translation:
>.. 行け！行け！ 
>.. どこに向かってるのか分からない！
>.. まだ来るぞ！ <size=200%><color=red>このクソ野郎どもから離れるんだ！</color></size>

Korean.Translation:
>.. 가! 빨리! 
>.. 가는 방향이 안 보여!
>.. 더 튀어나온다! <size=200%><color=red>염병! 도망가야 돼!</color></size>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…走開！走開！
>…我看不到前面的路！
>…還有更多！<size=200%><color=red>我們得遠離這該死的東西！</color></size>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 闪开！快！
>.. 我都看不见路！
>.. 越来越多了！<size=200%><color=red>我们得甩掉这个鬼东西！</color></size>

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_3_2.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
>.. I’m not touching the next one. <size=200%><color=red>You do it.</color></size>
>.. This whole place feels like it wants me dead.
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Je touche pas au prochain. <size=200%><color=red>Je te le laisse.</color></size>
>... J'ai l'impression que cet endroit veut ma mort.

Italian.Translation:
>... Io non tocco il prossimo. <size=200%><color=red>Fallo tu.</color></size>
>... Sembra che questo posto mi voglia morto.

German.Translation:
>… Das Nächste rühre ich nicht an. <size=200%><color=red>Ihr seid dran.</color></size>
>… Ich habe das Gefühl, dass dieser Ort mich tot sehen will.

Spanish.Translation:
> No voy a tocar el siguiente. <size=200%><color=red>Hazlo tú.</color></size>
> Parece que este lugar me quiere fuera.

Russian.Translation:
>... Я эту мерзость трогать не буду. <size=200%><color=red>Выполнять приказ.</color></size>
>... У меня дурное предчувствие. Мы тут все сдохнем.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Não vou tocar no próximo. <size=200%><color=red>É sua vez.</color></size>
>.. Este lugar inteiro parece querer que eu morra.

Polish.Translation:
>.. Nie tykam następnego. <size=200%><color=red>Sam to zrób.</color></size>
>.. Całe to miejsce chce mnie chyba ukatrupić.

Japanese.Translation:
>.. 次のやつには触らないぞ。 <size=200%><color=red>お前がやれ。</color></size>
>.. よってたかって殺しにかかってきやがる。

Korean.Translation:
>.. 다시는 안 만진다. <size=200%><color=red>만져야 될걸.</color></size>
>.. 이곳이 통째로 날 못 죽여 안달 난 것 같아.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…我才不要碰下一個。<size=200%><color=red>你去。</color></size>
>…這整個地方感覺像是要置我於死地。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 我不要碰下一个。<size=200%><color=red>动手。</color></size>
>.. 这整个地方感觉就想让我死。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_3_1.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
Prisoners sent to extract vital datacores from terminals in digsite.
Unknown ceiling dwelling biomass present. Prisoners failing to exercise caution will not be considered a loss.
Air filtration system unstable.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Expedition_1_3.Description

Blocks.English:
Prisoners sent to retrieve the matter wave protector in digsite.
Hostile creatures detected. Prisoners failing to exercise caution will not be considered a loss.
Blocks.name: RundownData.R6.Expedition_1.Description

Blocks.English:
>...Good news: The only thing between us and our way forward is that door.
>...And the bad news?
>...It's protected by a multilevel security system.
<size=200%><color=red>>...Less talk, more digging...</color></size>
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.
Blocks.name: RundownData.Expedition_1_3.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
>.. Christ don’t these bastards ever let up?
>.. Conserve your ammo!
<color=red>>.. Fuck that! I'm using everything I got!</color></size>
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Bordel, ils s'arrêtent jamais ou quoi ?!
>... Ne gaspille pas tes munitions !
<color=red>>... Et puis merde ! Je vais tirer tout ce qu'il me reste !</color></size>

Italian.Translation:
>... Cavolo, questi bastardi non mollano mai?
>... Risparmiamo le munizioni!
<color=red>>... Fanculo! Io uso tutto quello che ho!</color></size>

German.Translation:
>… Verdammt, lassen diese Bastarde denn nie locker?
>… Spart eure Munition!
<color=red>>… Was soll’s! Ich gebe alles, was ich habe!</color></size>

Spanish.Translation:
> ¿Es que no se cansan?
> ¡Conservad la munición!
<color=red>> ¡A la mierda, voy con todo!</color></size>

Russian.Translation:
>... Эта мразь хоть когда-нибудь отстанет?
>... Беречь боеприпасы!
<color=red>>... К черту! Я их напичкаю свинцом!</color></size>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Cara, esses desgraçados nunca param?
>.. Economize na munição!
<color=red>>.. Foda-se! Vou com tudo que eu tenho!</color></size>

Polish.Translation:
>.. Chryste, czy te gnojki nigdy się nie poddają?
>.. Oszczędzać amunicję!
<color=red>>.. Pierdolę to! Pruję, czym się da!</color></size>

Japanese.Translation:
>.. こいつら、諦めるってことを知らないのか？
>.. 弾を節約しろ！
<color=red>>.. 構っていられるか！ありったけ使ってやる！</color></size>

Korean.Translation:
>.. 좀 얌전히 뒈질 수 없나?
>.. 총알 아껴 써!
<color=red>>.. 좆까! 필요하면 몽땅 써야지!</color></size>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…天啊，這些混蛋一刻都不放鬆的嗎？
>…省省你的彈藥！
<color=red>>…操！我已經使盡全力了！</color></size>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 天啊，这些玩意儿没完没了的吗？
>.. 节省弹药！
<color=red>>.. 该死！我的要用光了！</color></size>

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_3_3.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.English:
>.. I’m not going into that shit. I don’t feel right…
<size=200%><color=red>>.. It just got a lot more fucking intense.</color></size>
>.. Let’s not wait around. Scan the thing.
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Je veux pas entrer dans ce bourbier. Je me sens pas bien...
<size=200%><color=red>>... C'est de pire en pire, bordel.</color></size>
>... Ne perdons pas de temps. Analyse ce truc.

Italian.Translation:
>... Io non entro in quello schifo. Non mi piace per niente...
<size=200%><color=red>>... È diventato tutto maledettamente più intenso.</color></size>
>... Non aspettiamo. Scansioniamo quella roba.

German.Translation:
>… Da mache ich nicht mit. Ich habe kein gutes Gefühl …
<size=200%><color=red>>… Das ist ja noch heftiger geworden.</color></size>
>… Wir sollten uns hier nicht lange aufhalten. Scannt das Ding.

Spanish.Translation:
> No entro ahí ni de coña. No me encuentro bien...
<size=200%><color=red>> Sí que se ha puesto intensa la cosa.</color></size>
> Venga, no perdamos más tiempo. Escanead esa cosa.

Russian.Translation:
>... Я в эту дыру не полезу. У меня плохое предчувствие...
<size=200%><color=red>>... С каждой минутой все напряженнее.</color></size>
>... Не теряем время. Проверь эту дрянь.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Não vou entrar naquela merda. Não confio…
<size=200%><color=red>>.. A coisa ficou muito pior.</color></size>
>.. Não vamos perder tempo. Escaneie o troço.

Polish.Translation:
>.. Nie pakuję się w to gówno. Kiepsko ze mną…
<size=200%><color=red>>.. No to się zrobił pierdolnik.</color></size>
>.. Nie czekajmy z założonymi rękami. Przeskanuj to.

Japanese.Translation:
>.. あそこには行かないぞ。嫌な予感がする…
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 状況が悪化しただけだな。</color></size>
>.. 待つのはやめよう。あれをスキャンしろ。

Korean.Translation:
>.. 난 죽어도 안 들어간다. 감이 안 좋아…
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 훨씬 더 심해졌잖아.</color></size>
>.. 뭉개고 있지 말고 스캔해.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…我才不要進去。感覺不對勁…
<size=200%><color=red>>…變得更激烈了。</color></size>
>…我們不要等了，快掃描。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 我不要进去那个鬼地方，感觉不对劲……
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 竟然比之前还要难搞多了。</color></size>
>.. 我们别浪费时间了，快扫描。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_2_2.RoleplayedWardenIntel

Blocks.Description: A text string shown in the HUD that informs the player that the part of the underground complex where the player current is, is in "mergency lockdown". This means that the door the player needs to go through in order to proceed, is locked until the lockdown is lifted.
Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.Header

Blocks.English: Find Computer terminal [ITEM_SERIAL] and find a way to lift the lockdown.
Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. Don't alter the "[ITEM_SERIAL]" part, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

French.Translation: Accédez au terminal informatique [ITEM_SERIAL] et trouvez un moyen de déverrouiller l'accès.

Italian.Translation: Trova il terminale computer [ITEM_SERIAL] e trova un modo per rimuovere l'isolamento.

German.Translation: Finden Sie den Computerterminal [ITEM_SERIAL] und einen Weg, die Abriegelung aufzuheben.

Spanish.Translation: Encuentra la terminal [ITEM_SERIAL] y averigua cómo anular el cierre de emergencia.

Russian.Translation: Найдите компьютерный терминал [ITEM_SERIAL] и отключите режим изоляции.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Encontre o terminal de computador [ITEM_SERIAL] e descubra uma maneira de desativar o confinamento.

Polish.Translation: Znajdź terminal komputerowy [ITEM_SERIAL] i spróbuj znieść blokadę.

Japanese.Translation: コンピュータ端末 [ITEM_SERIAL] を見つけて緊急封鎖を解く方法を探せ。

Korean.Translation: [ITEM_SERIAL] 컴퓨터 터미널을 찾아 폐쇄를 해제할 방법 찾기

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 找到電腦終端[ITEM_SERIAL]並找出解除封鎖的方法。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 找到电脑终端[ITEM_SERIAL]并想办法解除封锁。

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.MainObjective

Blocks.English: Gather information about the location of [ITEM_SERIAL]
Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. Don't alter the "[ITEM_SERIAL]" part, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

French.Translation: Obtenez plus d'information sur l'emplacement du [ITEM_SERIAL].

German.Translation: Sammeln Sie Informationen über den Standort von [ITEM_SERIAL].

Spanish.Translation: Recopila información sobre la ubicación de [ITEM_SERIAL].

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Colete informações sobre a localização de [ITEM_SERIAL].

Japanese.Translation: [ITEM_SERIAL]の場所に関する情報を集めろ

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.FindLocationInfo

Blocks.English: Access more data in the terminal maintenance system
Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. The player is encouraged to find more data by accessing computer terminals.

French.Translation: Obtenez plus de données dans le système de maintenance du terminal.

Italian.Translation: Accedi a ulteriori dati nel sistema di manutenzione del terminale

German.Translation: Greifen Sie auf mehr Daten im Terminal-Wartungssystem zu.

Spanish.Translation: Accede a más información con el sistema de mantenimiento de la terminal.

Russian.Translation: Найдите данные в системе управления терминалом.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Avalie mais dados no sistema de manutenção do terminal.

Polish.Translation: Uzyskaj dostęp do danych systemie serwisowym terminali.

Japanese.Translation: 端末のメンテナンスシステムで更に多くのデータにアクセスしろ

Korean.Translation: 터미널 유지 관리 시스템에서 더 많은 데이터에 접근

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 在終端維護系統中存取更多資料。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 访问更多终端维护系统中的数据。

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.FindLocationInfoHelp

Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. Don't alter the "[ITEM_ZONE/SERIAL]" parts, just put them in the gramatically correct positions in the sentence.

German.Translation: Begeben Sie sich zu [ITEM_ZONE] und finden Sie [ITEM_SERIAL].

Russian.Translation: Отправляйтесь в зону [ITEM_ZONE] и найдите предмет ([ITEM_SERIAL]).

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.GoToZone

Blocks.English: Use information in the environment to find [ITEM_ZONE]
Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. In GTFO you seldom get a waypoint that indicates where you need to go - instead you need to actively look for signs and clues in the surroundings. Don't alter the "[ITEM_ZONE]" part, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

French.Translation: Utilisez les informations dans la zone pour trouver [ITEM_ZONE].

Italian.Translation: Utilizza le informazioni ambientali per trovare [ITEM_ZONE]

German.Translation: Nutzen Sie Informationen in der Umgebung, um [ITEM_ZONE] zu finden.

Spanish.Translation: Usa información del entorno para encontrar [ITEM_ZONE].

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Use as informações no ambiente para encontrar [ITEM_ZONE].

Polish.Translation: Skorzystaj z informacji środowiskowych, aby znaleźć [ITEM_ZONE].

Japanese.Translation: 周囲の情報を手掛かりに [ITEM_ZONE]を見つけろ

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 使用環境中的資訊尋找[ITEM_ZONE]。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 利用环境中的信息找到[ITEM_ZONE]。

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.GoToZoneHelp

Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. Don't alter the "[ITEM_ZONE/SERIAL]" parts, just put them in the gramatically correct positions in the sentence.

French.Translation: Trouvez [ITEM_SERIAL] quelque part à l'intérieur de [ITEM_ZONE].

Japanese.Translation: [ITEM_SERIAL] を [ITEM_ZONE]の中のどこかで見つけろ

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.InZoneFindItem

Blocks.English: Use maintenance terminal command PING to find [ITEM_SERIAL]
Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. Don't alter the "[ITEM_SERIAL]" part, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence. "PING" is a computer terminal command and should NOT be translated.

French.Translation: Utilisez la commande PING du terminal de maintenance pour trouver [ITEM_SERIAL].

Italian.Translation: Utilizza il comando SEGNALA del terminale di manutenzione per trovare [ITEM_SERIAL]

German.Translation: Nutzen Sie den Befehl "ping" des Wartungsterminals, um [ITEM_SERIAL] zu finden.

Spanish.Translation: Usa el comando PING en la terminal de mantenimiento y encuentra [ITEM_SERIAL].

Russian.Translation: Используйте команду терминала PING, чтобы найти предмет ([ITEM_SERIAL]).

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Use o comando MARCA no terminal de manutenção para encontrar [ITEM_SERIAL].

Polish.Translation: Użyj polecenia PING w terminalu serwisowym, aby znaleźć [ITEM_SERIAL].

Japanese.Translation: メンテナンス端末のPINGコマンドを使用して [ITEM_SERIAL]を見つけろ

Korean.Translation: 유지관리 터미널 명령어 PING을 이용해 [ITEM_SERIAL] 찾기

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 使用維護終端指令PING尋找[ITEM_SERIAL]。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用维护终端命令PING找到[ITEM_SERIAL]。

Blocks.name: WardenObjectiveData.SpecialTerminalCommand_Override.InZoneFindItemHelp

Blocks.English: Proceed to input the backdoor command [SPECIAL_COMMAND] in [ITEM_SERIAL]
Blocks.Description: A short summary of a mission objective. "Input the backdoor command" is just a cool way to say you need to input a specific computer command in a terminal (the terminal ID will replace "[ITEM_SERIAL]".) Don't alter the "[SPECIAL_COMMAND]/[ITEM_SERIAL]" part, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

French.Translation: Entrez la commande de backdoor [SPECIAL_COMMAND] dans le [ITEM_SERIAL].

German.Translation: Fahren Sie mit der Eingabe des Hintertür-Befehls [SPECIAL_COMMAND] in [ITEM_SERIAL] fort.

Blocks.Description:
{0} is a value between 0 and 100
In GTFO you can find artifacts around the maps. If the "artifact heat" of a particular mission is high, the artifacts found on this mission will be valuable and can be exchanged for other valuable items. If the "artifact heat" is low, the artifacts will be less valuable. So the value of artifacts go up and down like a stock, and the term "artifact heat" represents the "exchange rate" (i.e. the current value) of the artifacts in a given mission.

Prigionieri inviati a recuperare Proiettore Onde Materia.

German.Translation:
Entkoppeltes System identifiziert und lokalisiert.
Gefangene wurden geschickt, um den Materiewellenprojektor zu holen.

Spanish.Translation:
Sistema sin acoplar identificado y ubicado.
Se han enviado prisioneros para recoger el proyector de ondas de materia [MATTER_WAVE_PROJECTOR].

Russian.Translation:
Обнаружена неподключенная система.
Заключенным поручено забрать проектор материальных волн [MATTER_WAVE_PROJECTOR].

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Sistema não acoplado identificado e localizado.
Prisioneiros enviados para coletar o projetor de onda de matéria.

Polish.Translation:
Zidentyfikowano i zlokalizowano niesprzężony system.
Więźniowie zostali wysłani w celu zebrania projektora fal materii.

Japanese.Translation:
分離システムを発見、特定。
マターウェーブプロジェクター回収のため、囚人を派遣した。

Korean.Translation:
분리된 시스템이 발견되었습니다.
물질파 투사기 회수를 위해 수감자들이 투입되었습니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
已識別並定位未耦合系統。
已派遣囚犯去收集物質波投影器。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
识别并定位到非耦合系统。
派出囚犯收集物质波放映机。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_1_1.Description

Blocks.English:
Locate terminal in Alpha Two and extract Data Cube coordinates.
Exotic environmental conditions.
Blocks.Description: Don't localize Data Cube.

French.Translation:
Localisez le terminal dans Alpha Deux et récupérez les coordonnées du cube de données [DATA_CUBE].
Conditions environnementales exotiques.

Italian.Translation:
Individuare il terminale in Alfa Due ed estrarre le coordinate del cubo di dati [DATA_CUBE].
Condizioni ambientali esotiche.

German.Translation:
Lokalisieren Sie das Terminal in Alpha Two und extrahieren Sie die Koordinaten des Datenwürfels [DATA_CUBE].
Außergewöhnliche Umweltbedingungen.

Spanish.Translation:
Encuentra una terminal en Alfa-2 y extrae las coordenadas del cubo de datos [DATA_CUBE].
Condiciones medioambientales: exóticas.

Russian.Translation:
Найдите терминал в Альфа-Два и извлеките координаты куба данных [DATA_CUBE].
Экзотические условия среды.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Localize o terminal no Alfa Dois e extraia as coordenadas do cubo de dados [DATA_CUBE].
Condições ambientais diferenciadas.

Polish.Translation:
Zlokalizuj terminal w Alfa 2 i pozyskaj współrzędne kostki danych.
Egzotyczne warunki środowiskowe.

Japanese.Translation:
アルファ2で端末を見つけ、データキューブ[DATA_CUBE]の座標を抽出しろ。
異国環境状態。

Korean.Translation:
알파 2에서 터미널을 찾아 [DATA_CUBE] 데이터 큐브 좌표를 확보하십시오.
특이 환경 조건에 주의해야 합니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
定位Alpha Two的終端並撤離資料方塊[DATA_CUBE]座標。
異域環境狀況。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
在阿尔法二找到终端并提取数据立方[DATA_CUBE]坐标。
环境条件异常。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_2_1.Description

Blocks.English:
>.. What the hell is this place?
>.. Are we alright to breathe this stuff?
<size=200%><color=red>>.. Ah shit, look up!</color></size>
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... C'est quoi cet endroit ?
>... On peut respirer ce truc ?
<size=200%><color=red>>... Bordel, regardez là-haut !</color></size>

Italian.Translation:
>... Che cavolo è questo posto?
>... Facciamo bene a respirare questa roba?
<size=200%><color=red>>... Ah merda, guardate in alto!</color></size>

German.Translation:
>… Was zur Hölle ist das für ein Ort?
>… Können wir dieses Zeug einatmen?
<size=200%><color=red>>… Ah verdammt, da oben!</color></size>

Spanish.Translation:
> ¿Dónde demonios estamos?
> ¿No nos pasará nada si respiramos esto?
<size=200%><color=red>> ¡Mierda, mirad arriba!</color></size>

Russian.Translation:
>... Что за странное место?
>... Эту штуку можно вдыхать?
<size=200%><color=red>>... Вот черт! Берегись!</color></size>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Quer merda de lugar é esse?
>.. Tudo bem se a gente respirar isso?
<size=200%><color=red>>.. Ah, droga, olhe para cima!</color></size>

Polish.Translation:
>.. Co to za miejsce, do diabła?!
>..Możemy to wdychać?
<size=200%><color=red>>..O psiamać, spójrzcie w górę!</color></size>

Japanese.Translation:
>.. ここはどうなってるんだ？
>.. これ、吸い込んで大丈夫なのか？
<size=200%><color=red>>.. クソ、見ろ！</color></size>

Korean.Translation:
>.. 여긴 대체 뭐야?
>.. 이거 숨 쉬어도 괜찮은 거야?
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 아, 제길! 조심해!</color></size>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…這是什麼鬼地方？
>…我們可以吸入這個嗎？
<size=200%><color=red>>…可惡，抬頭看！</color></size>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 这是个什么鬼地方？
>.. 我们吸入这东西没事吗？
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 糟糕，看上面！</color></size>

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_2_1.Roleplayed_Warden_Intel

Blocks.English: Conduit genetic code compromised. New DNA code required: Prisoners sent to locate HSU unit in order to retrieve DNA sample.
Blocks.Description: Don't localize HSU.

French.Translation: Code génétique du conduit compromis. Nouveau code ADN requis : les prisonniers ont été envoyés pour localiser l'unité HSU et récupérer un échantillon d'ADN.

Italian.Translation: Codice genetico condotto compromesso. Richiesto nuovo codice DNA: prigionieri inviati per localizzare la HSU e recuperare il campione di DNA.

German.Translation: Genetischer Code des Conduits kompromittiert. Neuer DNA-Code erforderlich: Gefangene wurden geschickt, um die HSU-Einheit zu lokalisieren und DNA-Proben sammeln zu können.

Spanish.Translation: Conducto de código genético en peligro. Se necesita nuevo código de ADN: se han enviado prisioneros para recoger la unidad de las HSU y que recuperen la muestra de ADN.

Russian.Translation: Ошибка генетического кода проводника. Требуется новый код ДНК. Заключенным поручено найти HSU и извлечь образец ДНК.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Código genético do conduto comprometido. Novo código de DNA necessário: prisioneiros enviados para localizar a unidade HSU a fim de recuperar a amostra de DNA.

Polish.Translation: Naruszono kod genetyczny przekaźnika. Wymagany nowy kod DNA: więźniowie zostali wysłani, aby zlokalizować zespół HSU i zdobyć próbkę DNA.

Japanese.Translation: コンジット遺伝子コード漏洩。新規DNAコードが必要：HSUユニットの位置を特定してDNAサンプルを回収するため囚人を派遣した。

Korean.Translation: 전달 유전 코드가 손상됐습니다. 새 DNA 코드가 필요합니다. DNA 샘플 확보를 위한 HSU 유닛을 찾기 위해 수감자들이 투입되었습니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 導管遺傳碼受損。需要新的DNA代碼：已派遣囚犯定位HSU裝置以擷取DNA樣本。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 导管遗传密码受损，需要新的DNA密码：派出囚犯定位HSU单元以取回DNA样本。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_2_2.Description

Blocks.English: Use extracted coordinates to retrieve 3 Data Cubes. Deviating energy readings detected in the related sector.
Blocks.Description: Don't localize Data Cubes.

French.Translation: Utilisez les coordonnées extraites pour récupérer 3 cubes de données. Des relevés d'énergie divergents ont été détectés dans le secteur concerné.

Italian.Translation: Usare le coordinate estratte per recuperare 3 cubi di dati [DATA_CUBE]. Rilevate tracce energetiche divergenti nel relativo settore.

German.Translation: Nutzen Sie die extrahierten Koordinaten, um 3 Datenwürfel [DATA_CUBE] zu finden. Abweichende Energiewerte im betreffenden Sektor festgestellt.

Spanish.Translation: Utiliza coordenadas extraídas para recuperar 3 cubos de datos [DATA_CUBE]. Se ha detectado un desvío en la lectura de energía del sector derivado.

Russian.Translation: Используйте полученные координаты и извлеките 3 куба данных [DATA_CUBE]. В соответствующем секторе обнаружены отклонения в показателях энергии.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Use as coordenadas extraídas para recuperar 3 cubos de dados [DATA_CUBE]. Leituras energéticas diferentes detectadas no setor relacionado.

Polish.Translation: Użyj pozyskanych współrzędnych, aby zdobyć 3 kostki danych [DATA_CUBE]. W powiązanym sektorze wykryto odchylenia w odczytach energii.

Japanese.Translation: 抽出した座標を使って3データキューブ[DATA_CUBE]を回収しろ。関連セクターで逸脱エネルギー反応を検出。

Korean.Translation: 확보한 좌표를 사용해 [DATA_CUBE] 데이터 큐브 3개를 찾으십시오. 관련 섹터에서 이상 에너지 신호가 감지됐습니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 使用撤離的座標取得3個資料方塊[DATA_CUBE]。在相關分區偵測到偏離的能源讀數。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用提取的坐标取回3个数据立方[DATA_CUBE]。相关分区中检测到偏离能量读数。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_3_1.Description

Blocks.English:
Translocation power requirements not met. Activation of auxiliary generators necessary.
Severe environmental conditions anticipated.

French.Translation:
Alimentation insuffisante pour la translocation. Les générateurs auxiliaires doivent être activés.
Risques d'environnement instable élevés.

Italian.Translation:
Requisiti energia trasferimento non soddisfatti. Richiesta attivazione generatori ausiliari.
Previste condizioni ambientali severe.

German.Translation:
Energieanforderungen für die Translokation nicht erfüllt. Aktivierung von Hilfsgeneratoren erforderlich.
Es werden strenge Umweltbedingungen erwartet.

Spanish.Translation:
No se cumplen los requisitos de energía de translocación. Deben activarse los generadores auxiliares.
Se esperan condiciones climatológicas graves.

Russian.Translation:
Требования к питанию пространственной связи не выполнены. Необходимо включение резервных генераторов.
Тяжелые условия окружающей среды.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Requisitos de força de translocação não atendidos. Necessária ativação de geradores auxiliares.
Condições ambientais severas antecipadas.

Polish.Translation:
Nie spełniono wymaganej mocy do translokacji. Wymagane uruchomienie pomocniczych generatorów.
Spodziewane skrajne warunki środowiskowe.

Japanese.Translation:
転移電力要件不足。予備発電機の起動が必要。
厳しい環境条件が予測される。

Korean.Translation:
전위에 필요한 전력이 부족합니다. 보조 발전기를 가동해야 합니다.
극단적인 환경 조건이 예상됩니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
未符合移位電源要求。必須啟用輔助發電機。
預計將有惡劣的環境狀況。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
易位电力要求未满足。需要启动备用发电机。
预计环境条件恶劣。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_3_2.Description

Blocks.English:
Prisoners will act as decoy for undisclosed parallel objective.
Surviving prisoners will return for extraction once undisclosed objective has been completed.

French.Translation:
Les prisonniers serviront de leurre pour un objectif parallèle tenu secret.
Les survivants retourneront au point d'extraction une fois l'objectif atteint.

Italian.Translation:
I prigionieri fungeranno da esca per un obiettivo parallelo segreto.
I prigionieri sopravvissuti torneranno per l'estrazione una volta che l'obiettivo segreto sarà stato completato.

German.Translation:
Gefangene dienen als Lockvogel für ein unbekanntes paralleles Ziel.
Überlebende Gefangene kehren zurück und werden abgeholt, sobald das unbekannte Ziel erreicht ist.

Spanish.Translation:
Los prisioneros harán de señuelo para el objetivo paralelo sin revelar.
Los prisioneros que sobrevivan regresarán al punto de extracción cuando se complete el objetivo sin revelar.

Russian.Translation:
Заключенные выполняют роль приманки для секретной дополнительной цели.
Выжившие заключенные вернутся в точку выхода, как только секретная цель будет выполнена.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Prisioneiros agirão como chamariz para objetivo paralelo confidencial.
Prisioneiros sobreviventes retornarão à extração após a conclusão do objetivo em questão.

Polish.Translation:
Więźniowie posłużą za przynętę dla nieujawnionego, równoległego celu.
Po osiągnięciu celu ocalali więźniowie powrócą, aby dokonać ewakuacji.

Japanese.Translation:
囚人たちは非公開の平行目標のおとりとして機能する。
生き残った囚人は、非公開の目標を完了すると脱出のために帰還する。

Korean.Translation:
수감자들은 비공개 병행 목표를 위한 미끼 역할을 합니다.
생존 수감자들은 비공개 목표 수행 후 탈출 지점으로 복귀할 것입니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
囚犯將充當未揭露平行目標的誘餌。
一旦未揭露的目標完成，倖存的囚犯將返回撤離點。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
囚犯将扮演不明并行目标的诱饵。
不明目标完成后，幸存的囚犯将立即返回撤离点。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_3_3.Description

Blocks.English:
Waypoint data confirmed. Primary Restoration Initiative has commenced. 
Dispatch prisoners to secure Pathogen Genome Database.

French.Translation:
Données de cheminement confirmées. Le programme de restauration principal a commencé.
Envoyez les prisonniers pour sécuriser la base de données du génome pathogène.

Italian.Translation:
Dati waypoint confermati. Avviata Iniziativa Restauro Primario. 
Inviare prigionieri per ottenere Database Genoma Patogeno.

German.Translation:
Wegpunktdaten bestätigt. Primäre Wiederherstellung wurde eingeleitet.
Schicken Sie Gefangene los, um die Pathogen-Gendatenbank zu sichern.

Spanish.Translation:
Datos de parada confirmados. Comienza la iniciativa de restauración primaria. 
Envía prisioneros para proteger la base de datos del genoma de patógenos.

Russian.Translation:
Данные маршрута подтверждены. Первичное восстановление начато. 
Отправьте заключенных, чтобы сохранить базу данных геномной информации патогена.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Dados do ponto de passagem confirmados. Iniciativa de restauração primária iniciada. 
Despache prisioneiros para proteger o banco de dados de genomas patogênicos.

Polish.Translation:
Potwierdzono dane punktu kontrolnego. Rozpoczęto inicjatywę w zakresie odbudowy podstawowej.
Wysłać więźniów w celu zabezpieczenia baza danych genomów patogenów.

Japanese.Translation:
通過点データを確認。主復元イニシアチブを開始。 
囚人を展開して病原体ゲノムデータベースを確保しろ。

Korean.Translation:
웨이포인트 데이터가 확인됐습니다. 주요 복구 절차가 시작됐습니다. 
수감자들을 보내 병원체 게놈 데이터베이스를 확보하십시오

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
已確認航路點資料。一級恢復計畫已展開。
派遣囚犯去取得病原體基因組資料庫。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
路径点数据已确认。一级恢复计划已开始。
派遣囚犯获取病原体基因组数据库。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_1.Description

Blocks.English:
>.. What's that? Is that a...
>.. Tha.. that's not possible!
>.. <size=200%><color=red>>We shouldn't be here</color></size>
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Qu'est-ce que c'est ? On dirait un...
>... Non... c'est pas possible !
>... <size=200%><color=red>>On devrait pas être ici.</color></size>

Italian.Translation:
>... Che cos'è? È un...
>... Non... non è possibile!
>... <size=200%><color=red>>Non dovremmo essere qui</color></size>

German.Translation:
>… Was ist das? Ist das …?
>… Da– Das ist unmöglich!
>… <size=200%><color=red>>… Wir sollten nicht hier sein.</color></size>

Spanish.Translation:
> ¿Qué es eso? ¿Es...?
> ¡No! ¡No puede ser!
> <size=200%><color=red>> ¡No deberíamos estar aquí!</color></size>

Russian.Translation:
>... Что это? Это же...
>... Но... Это невозможно!
>... <size=200%><color=red>>Надо валить отсюда.</color></size>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. O que era aquilo? Era...
>.. aquilo.. Não é possível!
>.. <size=200%><color=red>>A gente não devia estar aqui</color></size>

Polish.Translation:
>.. Co to takiego? Czy to...
>..To... to niemożliwe!
>.. <size=200%><color=red>>Nie powinno nas tu być</color></size>

Japanese.Translation:
>.. 何だ？まさか...
>.. あ.. ありえない！
>.. <size=200%><color=red>>ここを動かないほうがいい</color></size>

Korean.Translation:
>.. 저게 뭐야? 저거...
>.. 저건... 말도 안 돼!
>.. <size=200%><color=red>>여기 있으면 안 돼</color></size>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…那是什麼？那是…
>…那…那不可能！
>…<size=200%><color=red>>我們不應該來這裡</color></size>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 那是什么？那难道是……
>.. 这……这不可能！
>.. <size=200%><color=red>>我们不该来这里</color></size>

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_1.Roleplayed_Warden_Intel

Blocks.English:
Retrieve PGD decryption keys from multiple terminals.
Conditions unknown.

French.Translation:
Récupérez des clés de décryptage PGD sur plusieurs terminaux.
Conditions inconnues.

Italian.Translation:
Recuperare le chiavi di decrittazione PGD da più terminali.
Condizioni sconosciute.

German.Translation:
Besorgen Sie die PGD-Entschlüsselungscodes von mehreren Terminals.
Bedingungen unbekannt.

Spanish.Translation:
Recupera las claves de descifrado de la BDGP de varias terminales.
Condiciones: desconocidas.

Russian.Translation:
Извлеките ключи шифрования PGD из нескольких терминалов.
Условия неизвестны.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Recupere as chaves de decodificação PGD em diversos terminais.
Condições desconhecidas.

Polish.Translation:
Zdobądź klucze deszyfrujące z kilku terminali.
Warunki nieznane.

Japanese.Translation:
複数の端末からPGD解読キーを回収しろ。
状況は不明。

Korean.Translation:
여러 터미널에서 PGD 암호 키를 회수하십시오.
조건은 확인되지 않았습니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
從多個終端檢索PGD解碼密鑰。
狀況未知。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
从多个终端取回PGD解密密钥。
条件未知。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_2.Description

Blocks.English:
<size=200%><color=red>>.. Just get the data! </color></size>I can't wait to get out of here... 
>.. Yeah, but what's between us and the exit? Huh? 
>.. Can't be worse than this!
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>... On doit juste récupérer les données ! </color></size>J'ai hâte de sortir d'ici... 
>... Ouais, mais qu'est-ce qu'il y a entre nous et la sortie ? Hein ? 
>... Ça pourra pas être pire !

Italian.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>... Prendete i dati! </color></size>Non vedo l'ora di uscire di qui... 
>... Già, ma cosa c'è tra noi e l'uscita? Eh? 
>... Non può essere peggio di così!

German.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>… Besorgt einfach die Daten! </color></size>Ich kann es kaum erwarten, hier rauszukommen …
>… Ja, aber was liegt zwischen uns und dem Ausgang? Hm?
>… Schlimmer kann es nicht werden!

Spanish.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>> ¡Coged los datos! </color></size>Qué ganas de largarme de aquí... 
> Sí, pero ¿qué se interpone entre nosotros y la salida? ¿Eh? 
> ¡No puede ser peor que esto!

Russian.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>... Быстрее забирай данные! </color></size>Поскорее бы отсюда свалить... 
>... Да, но ты в курсе, что стоит на пути к выходу? А? 
>... Хуже уже не будет!

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>.. Pegue só os dados! </color></size>Não vejo a hora de sair daqui... 
>.. Sim, mas o que tem entre nós e a saída, hein? 
>.. Não pode ser pior do que isso!

Polish.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>.. Zdobądźcie po prostu dane! </color></size>Nie mogę się doczekać, aż się stąd wyniesiemy... 
>..Tak, ale co czeka między nami a punktem ewakuacji? 
>.. Nic gorszego niż to!

Japanese.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>.. いいからデータを手に入れろ！ </color></size>早くここから抜け出したい... 
>.. ああ、だが出口の前には何が待ってる？ 
>.. ここよりはマシだ！

Korean.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 일단 데이터 챙겨! </color></size>빨리 여기서 나가야 해... 
>.. 그래, 그런데 출구 앞에 뭐가 있지 않아? 
>.. 정말 최악이구만!

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>…剛剛取得資料！</color></size>我等不及要趕快離開了…
>…對，但是出口之前還會碰到什麼？嗯？
>…不會比這個更糟！

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
<size=200%><color=red>>.. 快把数据拿来！</color></size>我恨不得马上离开这里……
>.. 嗯，但隔在我们和出口之间的是什么？哈？
>.. 不会比这个更糟糕！

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_2.Roleplayed_Warden_Intel

Blocks.English:
Additional power needed for data decryption.
Quadrant reactor requires start-up.

French.Translation:
Alimentation supplémentaire requise pour le décryptage des données.
Le réacteur du quadrant doit être démarré.

Italian.Translation:
Richiesta energia aggiuntiva per decifratura dati.
Richiesto riavvio reattore quadrante.

German.Translation:
Für die Entschlüsselung der Daten wird mehr Energie benötigt.
Der Quadrantenreaktor muss gestartet werden.

Spanish.Translation:
Se necesita energía adicional para el descifrado de datos.
Debe arrancarse el reactor del cuadrante.

Russian.Translation:
Для расшифровки данных требуется дополнительное питание.
Необходимо включить реактор сектора.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Energia adicional necessária para decodificação de dados.
Necessária inicialização do reator do quadrante.

Polish.Translation:
Odszyfrowanie danych wymaga dodatkowej mocy.
Reaktor w kwadrancie wymaga uruchomienia.

Japanese.Translation:
データ解読には追加電源が必要。
四分リアクターの始動が必要。

Korean.Translation:
데이터 암호화에 추가 전력 필요.
사분 반응로 가동이 필요합니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
資料解碼需要的額外電力。
象限反應器需要啟動。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
数据解密需要更多电力。
象限反应堆需要启动。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_3.Description

Blocks.English:
>.. Man! We're between a rock... <size=200%><color=red>and a fucked up place!</color></size>
>.. What if we split up? 
>.. I don't like it... but let's do it.
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>.... Bordel ! On est coincés... <size=200%><color=red>dans cet enfer !</color></size>
>... Et si on se séparait ? 
>... Ça me plaît pas beaucoup... mais d'accord.

Italian.Translation:
>... Dannazione! Siamo bloccati tra un'incudine... <size=200%><color=red>e un posto di merda!</color></size>
>... E se ci separassimo? 
>... Non mi piace... ma facciamolo.

German.Translation:
>… Wir befinden uns zwischen einem Felsen … <size=200%><color=red>und einem richtig beschissenen Ort!</color></size>
>… Und wenn wir uns aufteilen?
>… Das gefällt mir nicht … aber uns bleibt keine Wahl.

Spanish.Translation:
> Estamos entre una piedra... <size=200%><color=red>¡y un lugar de mierda!</color></size>
> ¿Y si nos dividimos?
> No me convence, pero... habrá que hacerlo.

Russian.Translation:
>... Ну и дела! Мы застряли между молотом... <size=200%><color=red>и преисподней!</color></size>
>... А если разделиться? 
>... Не нравится мне эта идея... Но давай попробуем.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. Cara! Estamos entre uma pedra... <size=200%><color=red>e um lugar bem zoado!</color></size>
>.. E se cada um for para um lado? 
>.. Não gostei da ideia... mas vamos nessa.

Polish.Translation:
>.. O rany! Jesteśmy między młotem a... <size=200%><color=red>pokurwionym miejscem!</color></size>
>.. Może powinniśmy się rozdzielić? 
>.. Nie podoba mi się... ale niech będzie.

Japanese.Translation:
>.. クソ！岩と... <size=200%><color=red>クソッタレな場所の間に挟まれちまった！</color></size>
>.. 二手に分かれてみるのはどうだ？ 
>.. 気乗りはしないが... やってみよう。

Korean.Translation:
>.. 젠장! 오도가도 못하게 됐잖아... <size=200%><color=red>좆 됐다고!</color></size>
>.. 나눠서 움직이면 어때? 
>.. 내키진 않지만... 해보자.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…天啊！我們卡在一塊石頭…<size=200%><color=red>和一個可怕的地方之間！</color></size>
>…要分頭進行嗎？
>…我感覺不太妙…但還是這麼辦吧。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 唉！前面是岩石……<size=200%><color=red>后面是暴乱现场！</color></size>
>.. 我们分头行动怎么样？
>.. 我觉得不太好……但就这么做吧。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_3.Roleplayed_Warden_Intel

Blocks.English:
Prisoners sent to retrieve Tampered Data Cube from Insight labs. 
Deviating energy readings detected. 
Very low prisoner survival rate expected.
Blocks.Description: Don't localize Tampered Data Cube.

French.Translation:
Les prisonniers ont été envoyés pour récupérer le cube de données altéré [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] dans le laboratoire d'Insight.
Relevés d'énergie divergents détectés.
Chances de survie des prisonniers : très faibles.

Italian.Translation:
Prigionieri inviati per recuperare cubo dati manomesso [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] dai laboratori Insight. 
Rilevate tracce energetiche divergenti. 
Previsto tasso di sopravvivenza prigionieri molto basso.

German.Translation:
Gefangene wurden geschickt, um den Manipulierten Datenwürfel [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] von Insight labs zu holen.
Abweichende Energiewerte festgestellt.
Erwartete Überlebensrate der Gefangenen äußerst gering.

Spanish.Translation:
Se han enviado prisioneros para recuperar el cubo de datos corrupto [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] de los laboratorios de información. 
Desvío de lecturas de energía detectado. 
Se prevé una tasa de supervivencia de los prisioneros mínima.

Russian.Translation:
Заключенным поручено извлечь испорченный куб данных [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] из лабораторий Insight. 
Обнаружены отклонения в показателях энергии. 
Ожидается низкая вероятность выживания заключенных.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Prisioneiros enviados para recuperar o cubo de dados adulterado [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] nos laboratórios Insight. 
Leituras energéticas diferentes detectadas. 
Taxa muito baixa de sobrevivência de prisioneiros esperada.

Polish.Translation:
Więźniowie zostali wysłani, aby zdobyć zmanipulowaną kostkę danych z laboratorium projektu Insight. 
Wykryto odchylenia w odczytach energii. 
Spodziewany bardzo niski wskaźnik przeżywalności.

Japanese.Translation:
インサイト・ラボから改竄データキューブ[TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE]を回収するために囚人を派遣した。 
逸脱エネルギー反応を検出。 
予想される囚人生存率：非常に低い。

Korean.Translation:
인사이트 랩에서 [TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE] 변조 데이터 큐브를 회수하기 위해 수감자들이 파견됐습니다.
이상 에너지 신호가 감지됐습니다.
수감자 생존 확률이 매우 낮을 것으로 예상됩니다.

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
已派遣囚犯去Insight實驗室取回遭竄改資料方塊[TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE]。
偵測到偏離的能量讀數。
囚犯的預期存活率非常低。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
派出囚犯从Insight实验室取回篡改的数据立方[TAMPERED_DATA_CUBE]。
检测到偏离能量读数。
预计囚犯存活率极低。

Blocks.name: RundownData.R6_Expedition_4_4.Description

Blocks.English:
>.. Not again.
>.. Hang on a sec… <size=200%><color=red>something's different</color></size>. 
>.. You're saying we're not gonna die? Has that fucking changed?
Blocks.Description: Warden Intel messages like these, with the >... symbols, are transcriptions of voice recordings.

French.Translation:
>... Pas encore.
>... Attendez une seconde... <size=200%><color=red>quelque chose a changé</color></size>. 
>... Qu'est-ce qui a changé ? Tu crois qu'on va survivre, c'est ça ?!

Italian.Translation:
>... Non di nuovo.
>... Aspetta un attimo... <size=200%><color=red>C'è qualcosa di diverso</color></size>. 
>... Vuoi dire che non moriremo? È cambiato?

German.Translation:
>…  Nicht schon wieder.
>… Moment mal … <size=200%><color=red>irgendetwas ist anders</color></size>. 
>… Das heißt, wir werden nicht sterben? Hat sich das verdammt noch mal geändert?

Spanish.Translation:
> Otra vez no...
> Un momento... <size=200%><color=red>Ha cambiado algo</color></size>.
> Entonces, ¿no vamos a morir? ¿Es eso lo que ha cambiado?

Russian.Translation:
>... Только не это.
>... Погоди-ка... <size=200%><color=red>В этот раз что-то изменилось</color></size>. 
>... То есть мы для разнообразия не сдохнем? Ты на это намекаешь?

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
>.. De novo não.
>.. Espere aí… <size=200%><color=red>algo está diferente</color></size>. 
>.. Está falando que não vamos morrer? Aquela merda mudou?

Polish.Translation:
>.. Tylko nie znowu.
>..Chwila... <size=200%><color=red>coś jest nie tak</color></size>. 
>.. Czy to znaczy, że nie umrzemy? Czy chociaż to się, kurwa, zmieniło?

Japanese.Translation:
>.. またか。
>.. ちょっと待て… <size=200%><color=red>何かがおかしい</color></size>. 
>.. 俺たちは助かるって？状況は変わったのか？

Korean.Translation:
>.. 또 이럴 순 없어.
>.. 잠깐 기다려… <size=200%><color=red>뭐가 좀 달라</color></size>. 
>.. 우리가 안 죽을 수도 있다는 거야? 씨발, 그런 거냐고?

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
>…別又來了。
>…等等…<size=200%><color=red>感覺不太一樣</color></size>。
>…你是說我們不會死嗎？這個事實他媽的改變了嗎？

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
>.. 别又来啊。
>.. 等等……<size=200%><color=red>有哪里不一样</color></size>。
>.. 你是说我们不会死吗？这一点有改变吗？
